                      throws IOException,

        Import an XML descriptor and use it as the model.
        Parameters:
        descriptor - String path to the XML descriptor file
        byName - if true then import the descriptor by name rather than a literal path
        paramValues - Optional parameter values to set after initializing
        Throws:
        IOException - if there is an error reading the file at the descriptor path
        org.apache.uima.util.InvalidXMLException - if there is an error parsing the xml of the descriptor
